.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 eztoc-toggle-hide-by-default' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/nwu-application-form-2024\/#What_to_Know_About_the_North-West_University_Application_Form_Portal\" title=\"What to Know About the North-West University Application Form Portal\">What to Know About the North-West University Application Form Portal<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/nwu-application-form-2024\/#Who_is_Eligible_to_Apply_for_Admission\" title=\"Who is Eligible to Apply for Admission\">Who is Eligible to Apply for Admission<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/nwu-application-form-2024\/#How_to_Apply_NWU_Application_Form_2024\" title=\"How to Apply | NWU Application Form 2024\">How to Apply | NWU Application Form 2024<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-4\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/nwu-application-form-2024\/#North-West_University_Application_Required_Documents\" title=\"North-West University Application Required Documents\">North-West University Application Required Documents<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-5\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/nwu-application-form-2024\/#Closing_Date\" title=\"Closing Date\">Closing Date<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p><strong>\u00a0<\/strong>To apply for admission into the North-West University NWU Application Form 2024, kindly follow the <a href=\"http:\/\/distance.nwu.ac.za\/apply-online\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">link<\/a> and apply online. All applications must be submitted online<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"what-to-know-about-the-north-west-university-application-form-portal\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"What_to_Know_About_the_North-West_University_Application_Form_Portal\"><\/span>What to Know About the North-West University Application Form Portal<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>The North-West University NWU Application portal is designed to accept application of candidates seeking for admission into the University. In the portal, applicant can Purchase application form, Track and monitor application status<a href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\">,<\/a> pay fees, Print Acknowledgement Slip, check admission list, etc.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"who-is-eligible-to-apply-for-admission\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Who_is_Eligible_to_Apply_for_Admission\"><\/span>Who is Eligible to Apply for Admission<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To be eligible for admission in the NWU application portal, candidates must;<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Have Secondary School Leaving Certificate<\/li>\n<li>Meet National Senior Certificate (NSC) requirement for admission into Higher Certificate<\/li>\n<li>Grade 12 certificate applicant is of added advantage<\/li>\n<li>Must write the NBTs for admission to NWU on\/before 15 October 2024.<\/li>\n<li>FPS of 480 or above.<\/li>\n<li>NBT scores of Upper<\/li>\n<li>Intermediate for AL &amp; QL<\/li>\n<li>Mathematics 60%<\/li>\n<li>English HL 50%<\/li>\n<li>English FAL 60%<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-apply-nwu-application-form-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_NWU_Application_Form_2024\"><\/span>How to Apply | NWU Application Form 2024<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Eligible candidates can <a href=\"http:\/\/distance.nwu.ac.za\/apply-online\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">click here to apply<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>Follow the steps below<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit Application portal<\/li>\n<li>Choose type of Application (Undergraduate, Post Graduate, Semester Studies)<\/li>\n<li>Fill and complete all necessary pages<\/li>\n<li>Pay Application fees where required<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-9033\" src=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/07\/apply.zp141926-300x180.webp\" alt=\"NWU Application Form 2024 | North-West University\" width=\"300\" height=\"180\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h2 id=\"north-west-university-application-required-documents\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"North-West_University_Application_Required_Documents\"><\/span><strong>North-West University Application Required Documents<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>To apply to NWU you need to submit the following documentation:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>A completed application form<\/li>\n<li>A copy of your results for the latest school year<\/li>\n<li>A copy of your ID<\/li>\n<li>If you have attended another higher education institution, we need a copy of your academic transcript<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2 id=\"closing-date\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Closing_Date\"><\/span>Closing Date<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>July 31, 2024<\/p>\n<p>For more information regarding the application for admission into the North-West University, kindly drop your messages in the comment box below.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"NWU Application Form 2024, North-West University Application 2024, NWU Online Application 2024 Opening Date, NWU Online Application 2024&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/9028"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"